data.description: Charming home sitting on 2.98 acres.  You don't have to worry about any HOA because there is none!  This beautiful one story all brick home has 3 bedroom,  2 baths.  Family room, living room and kitchen have a nice open floor plan.  Fireplace with gas logs, screened in porch, solid surface counter tops in the kitchen, onsite built cabinets, master suite with private bath, stainless steel appliances, shed , and dog kennel.  This home has so much to offer.  Animals allowed.  Just minutes from Lake Wateree.  $3,000 in closing cost if using Bill Oliver with Cardinal Financial.  Office 803-753-1623 and mobile 803-312-1800.
